Bagels | Not perfect looking, but not bad for my first ever bagel attempt! We had bagels for breakfast every single day during our trip to NYC and I'm happy to be able to recreate NYC style bagels at home. Much needed to fuel my travel wanderlust during these times. ☺️☺️☺️ #homemadebagels #nycbagels #bagelsandwich #bagelporn  #everythingbutthebagel #traderjoesfinds #traderjoesrecipes #isolationbaking #weekendbaking #bakersofsgp #bakersofinstagram #thebakefeed #bakefromscratch #stayhomebaking #circuitbreakersg #stayhomesg #sgigfoodie #手作りパン #weekendisobakeclub
@inhappenstance thank you! Yes making bagels was not as intimidating as I thought. Took so long for me to finally try it as there seemed to be so many steps involved. 😅😅

Great toppings and love the crumb! Congrats on your first bagel attempts 👏🏻👏🏻 it was my first attempt too! Thanks for joining us for #weekendisobakeclub. 💖💖💖 I can’t wait  to eat more bagels tomorrow. 🙋🏻‍♀️
